<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-9a39a77 elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-height-min-height elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-items-middle" data-e-type="section" data-element_type="section" data-id="9a39a77" data-settings='{"background_background":"classic"}'><div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no"><div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-15552466" data-e-type="column" data-element_type="column" data-id="15552466"><div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9db5168 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="9db5168" data-widget_type="heading.default"><h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">BIO</h3></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-aafb4e7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="aafb4e7" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><p class="p1"><span class="s2">Hello, I'm Elizabeth Arnau, a multidisciplinary creative born in Barcelona.</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">Imagination has always been at the heart of everything I do — I've been drawing and designing since I was a little girl. In 2005, I turned that passion into a career as a fashion designer, presenting collections in Barcelona, Cannes, China and at New York Fashion Week, before expanding into an international career in modeling and acting.</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">Today, my artistic vision extends behind the camera, where I lead the creative direction of fashion, beauty and lifestyle campaigns, creating photography, videography, illustration and AI-powered visuals for leading brands.</span></p></div><div style="width: 100%; max-width: 1000px; margin: 16px auto 60px;"><img src="/assets/images/2026/01/ClientsandPartnerships.jpg" alt="Clients &amp; Partnerships" style="width:100%; height:auto; display:block;" loading="lazy"></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1ea5710 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="1ea5710" data-widget_type="heading.default"><h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><span data-elementor-setting-key="title" data-pen-placeholder="Teclea aquí..." style="font-style: normal;clear: both">EXHIBITIONS &amp; AWARDS</span></h3></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e2a667a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="e2a667a" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><ul style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em;"><li>Art Exhibition, WeWork Glòries, Barcelona (2020)</li><li>The Golden Thimble Award, Madrid (2015)</li><li>Haute Couture Fashion Show, L'Illa Diagonal, Barcelona (2013)</li><li>Art Exhibition, Fundació Joan Miró, Barcelona (2011)</li><li>Charity Fashion Show with Hello Kitty, Barcelona (2011)</li><li>Cannes Fashion Week (2011)</li><li>New York Fashion Week (2010)</li><li>China Fashion Week (2009)</li></ul></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ed8dbf0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="ed8dbf0" data-widget_type="heading.default"><h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default" style="margin-top: 60px;">PRESS</h3></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0ae2a9f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="0ae2a9f" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0cm 0cm 11.25pt 0cm; font-size: 18px;">Elizabeth Arnau has been published in several press such as: Robb Report, Hola.com, Vanidad, FHM, The Bay Fashion, RB Fashion, Elega