38 125 325 129 313 142 300 154 292 171 292 187 292 204 296 221 308 233L563 492 304 771C292 783 288 800 288 817 288 833 296 850 308 863 321 871 338 875 354 875 371 875 388 867 400 854L696 533Z"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4542526 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="4542526" data-widget_type="spacer.default"><div class="elementor-spacer"><div class="elementor-spacer-inner"></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-17ca752 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="17ca752" data-widget_type="heading.default"><h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><span class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default elementor-inline-editing pen" data-elementor-setting-key="title" data-pen-placeholder="Teclea aquí..." style="font-style: normal;clear: both">SERVICES</span></h3></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b7411b5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-e-type="widget" data-element_type="widget" data-id="b7411b5" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">CREATIVE DIRECTION</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">Art direction and creative concepts for fashion, beauty and lifestyle campaigns &mdash; from the initial idea to the final visual execution, ensuring every detail reflects the brand&rsquo;s identity.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">MODELING &amp; ACTING</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">Fashion and commercial modeling &mdash; bringing the same artistic vision in front of the camera that I bring behind it. Acting for film, television, streaming and theatre productions.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">CONTENT CREATION</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">Ongoing photography, videography and illustrated content for fashion, beauty and lifestyle brands &mdash; from single productions to full content calendars, tailored to each platform and campaign.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">SOCIAL MEDIA MANAGEMENT</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">Creative strategy, content planning and day-to-day management of social media accounts, helping brands build a distinctive and engaging online presence.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">FASHION DESIGN &amp; STYLING</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">Fashion design and personal styling &mdash; from bespoke collections to editorial and red carpet looks, tailored to each client or campaign.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">ADVERTISING</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">I create tailor-made illustrations and visual concepts for fashion, beauty and lifestyle advertising, aligned with each brand&rsquo;s identity across both still and animated formats.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">My commissioned artwork has been used across social media, packaging, product design, storyboards, magazines, book covers, websites, merchandise, and print, digital and TV campaigns.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">CHARACTER DESIGN</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">Original characters designed for brands, packaging and campaigns, each with a distinct personality and style.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">STORE WINDOW DESIGN</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">Eye-catching artwork and design concepts for window displays and retail installations.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">ANIMATED SHORT FILMS</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">I bring my illustrated characters to life through animation, creating captivating short films where storytelling, fashion and imagination come together.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">LIVE EVENTS</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">Fast live illustration of guests at Fashion Weeks, press events, product launches, in-store activations, luxury events and private celebrations, including weddings, bridal showers, bachelorette parties and more.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">LICENSING</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">My existing artwork is available for licensing across homeware, décor, stationery, apparel, accessories and more.</p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold;">PRIVATE COMMISSIONS</span></p><p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: normal; text-align: justify;">Bespoke illustrations and portraits in my signature style &mdash; a timeless gift for life&rsquo;s most special occasions.</p></div></div></div></div></section>